elements.content: Everything You Didn't Know About Los Angeles
By Billy Rogers 08/11/20

resource.alt: Cars parked on gray concrete near trees

elements.content: Los Angeles, one of the most traveled cities in the world. But just when you thought you knew it all.
Here are 6 things you (probably) didn’t know.
BUNKER HILL
Downtown used to be the infamous Bunker Hill.
01.
The historic home of Los Angeles mobsters & the underground elite.

elements.content: An area of the city with roots in Hollywood film noir and beyond.
